Consider I\mathrel {\trianglelefteq } R being a maximal ideal of R by Krull's theorem. Then we know R/I is field, let us call it
\mathbb {F} := R/I.
We also have a surjective ring morphism R\twoheadrightarrow \mathbb {F}. Let
