A question we should never ask ourselves ever: Given we can work with complex matrices \mathop {\mathrm {Mat}}
olimits _{n}(\mathbb {C}), but we often find ourselves in many applications caring about rational matrices \mathop {\mathrm {Mat}}
olimits _{n}(\mathbb {Q}). For example if we have two matrices A,B\in \mathop {\mathrm {Mat}}
